Sure, here are some popular travel websites that offer competitive rates for hotels in Argos:

1. Booking.com
2. Expedia
3. Hotels.com
4. Agoda
5. TripAdvisor
6. Trivago
7. Kayak
8. Priceline
9. Orbitz
10. Travelocity

Keep in mind that some of these websites may offer additional discounts or promotions if you sign up for their loyalty programs or subscribe to their email newsletters. It's always a good idea to compare prices across multiple travel websites to make sure you're getting the best deal.
